SCANDINAVIA WHICH WILL CONTINUE TO SLWY SINK SWARDS INTO THE MAINLAND OF
CONTINENTAL EUROPE FM WEDNESDAY ONWARDS. MEANWHILE A COMPLEX AREA OF LOW
