WHICH IS EXP TO PUSH FRONTAL SYSTEMS N AND EWARDS ACROSS THE WHOLE OF THE
UK DURING THE EARLY PART OF THE WEEK. HOWEVER A RIDGE OF HIGH PRESSURE LOOKS
SET TO BUILD FM THE SW WHICH IS LIKELY TO EXTEND ACROSS THE SERN HALF OF
